about.desone: We're an international non-profit founded in 2003, with offices in London, New York, New Delhi, Amsterdam and Beijing.In that time, we’ve grown our network to include over 500 multinational businesses in 175 markets worldwide.We also work closely with governments at all levels. The Under2 Coalition, for which we are the Secretariat, is made up of 167 state and regional governments and has been named one of the international cooperative initiatives with the highest potential for emissions reductions.
